{"tid":327572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人如果冇感情嘅話會唔會仲好？","createTime":"2017-07-19T00:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T03:43:02.000Z","uid":8189,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"314be7f0836ef0e02b407e7b5827dd78fcf646d2","tid":327572,"uid":8189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:58:52.000Z","msg":"正所謂針冇兩頭利，每樣野都有利有害，感情帶畀人類好多歡樂，同時亦帶畀人類好多哀傷，如果畀我揀，我我寧願放棄歡樂同時避免哀傷<br />\n巴絲們點揀？"},{"pid":"9e745eb2e7fa19559219fe5cf1acc6024689da48","tid":327572,"uid":8189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"97b1af80a8edf8575f11778dbfcbe38b1ea03095","tid":327572,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:36:10.000Z","msg":"好似又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a80dfcede835b052835fa1bfc6f6c690ed3e83","tid":327572,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:02:47.000Z","msg":"咁會冇好多嘢"},{"pid":"878363e3bb48f8740ea034f58369460197a84580","tid":327572,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:15:59.000Z","msg":"本來生活得唔開心嘅人咪會覺得好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda087b8d40dcdbc25e451a9e5fa85effac9093b","tid":327572,"uid":8189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"究竟同時擁有快樂同哀傷好定係同時缺乏快樂同哀傷好？人冇感情嘅話，可能會同機械人冇分別，但係同機械人冇分別係唔係一定係壞事呢？"},{"pid":"1bcf4de77763a94417bd80c3de0928a6121eb670","tid":327572,"uid":21104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:10:04.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我覺得同人點解要存在一樣。<br />\n<br />\n學術角度嚟講，人如果冇感情呢個假設本身就唔係咁恰當，情緒本身已經係生物進化過程中留低嘅嘢，如果無用一早就比基因淘汰咗。<br />\n<br />\n人本身係一種動物，動物當然會有情感；就算感情無用，佢都係人嘅一個屬性，無情緒人生又邊有樂趣呢。<br />\n<br />\n以上都係我鳩嗡，有錯請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a5c7b9c745f5f1ee66e5661cab59de369e3c03","tid":327572,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"睇你點平衡"},{"pid":"24a9644f1cdfda66c00e7d0c79bedcf97ee41e4d","tid":327572,"uid":111531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"你咁樣諗同啲野生動物有咩分別？<br />\n正常人冇感情基本上會痴線"}]}